# Images Directory

Place your product images and assets in this directory.

## Recommended Images

### Homepage
- `hero-banner.jpg` - Main hero image (1920x800px)
- `feature-*.png` - Feature icons (64x64px)

### Products
- Product images should be named: `product-{id}.jpg`
- Recommended size: 800x800px
- Thumbnail size: 300x300px

### Crafts & Artisans
- `craft-*.jpg` - Craft category images (600x400px)
- `artisan-*.jpg` - Artisan profile photos (400x400px)

### Blog
- `blog-*.jpg` - Blog post featured images (800x500px)

## Image Optimization Tips
- Use WebP format for better compression
- Optimize images before uploading
- Use appropriate dimensions for different contexts
- Consider lazy loading for better performance
